    "Paper StructureSection II describes our method, including the use of LLM tools, Section III discusses the findings from exploration using GPT-4, Section IV and V discusses the findings from literature screening using Gemma 2:9b and full-text analysis using Claude 3.5 Sonnet, and Section VI summarizes all the findings, including an analysis to the research methodology we use, and recommends for the future research directions.This paper presents two distinct methodologies for LLMassisted literature surveys: Method A using ChatGPT 4 for initial exploration and thematic analysis, and Method B combining Gemma 2:9b for literature screening with Claude 3.5 Sonnet for full-text analysis.",
    "We compare these approaches to demonstrate their effectiveness in processing large volumes of academic literature efficiently.",
    "We employ two distinct LLM-assisted approaches: 1) Method A: GPT-4 for initial exploration and thematic analysis.",
    "2) Method B: Gemma 2:9b for literature screening and Claude 3.5 Sonnet for full-text analysis.",
